balls: - fixed bounce of rects - added rebound buff - added gameover check and screen - fixed bug that set the start point of still spawning balls to the location of the first ball which crashed. it will only happen on the next shot.

balls: - additional fix for collision with edges of rects (collision now done after the reaction as well, to see if the reaction was kinda correct) - fixed clicking without moving - added an simple way of handling an event moving over the screen (startcondition, condition, postevent and reset) - buffs now hold a gradient from magenta to yellow - added bars to indicate the numbers for rebounds and balls - moved spawning of buffs in front of rects so that the chance is actually defined and more likely on mobile (less place for rects)
